race.description: Brj Accountants & Business Advisors F&M Mdn Hcp
race.comment: TAGA SMILE (7) wasn't too far away at Tamworth on debut before being tipped out for further time to furnish. Has since returned with a runner-up finish at Gunnedah and will have derived a stack of benefit from that hit-out. Rates the testing material. WATCHYA LANGUAGE (2) is on debut but has shown ability at the trials and gets some weight off from the inside alley. Ticks a few boxes. MAKING EYES (8) gets the reliable Vandyke/Maloney combination and is capable of sharp improvement without surprising. ZOUBLIME (4) resumes here but showed glimpses of form when last in work and can run a big race while fresh. CAIRO QUEEN (9) strips fitter third-up from the spell and may earn some minor money.
